txt.en: The dangerous encampment Skrithûrz-ulíma is full of Orcs, presenting another deadly pocket in Zelem-melek.
The dangerous encampment Skrithûrz-ulíma is full of Orcs, presenting another deadly pocket in Zelem-melek.
The White-hand Orcs of Khazad-dûm can be found in great number in Skrithûrz-ulíma, near the centre of Zelem-melek.\n\nThe time has come to strike a critical blow against Moria's Orcs.
You have devastated the presence of Orcs in Skrithûrz-ulíma, making one small pocket of Zelem-melek less treacherous for the vulnerable expedition.
